yle=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #f8fafc;\" data-kid=\"83\">Suporte magnético</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"badge badge-electric\" data-kid=\"84\">79</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0;\" data-kid=\"85\">\n                    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;\" data-kid=\"86\">\n                      <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); font-weight: 700; width: 16px;\" data-kid=\"87\">03</span>\n                      <span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #f8fafc;\" data-kid=\"88\">Luminária gamer RGB</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"badge badge-ember\" data-kid=\"89\">71</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div style=\"background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;\" data-kid=\"90\">\n                  <div style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #94a3b8; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-kid=\"91\">Tendência do Nicho</div>\n                  \n                  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 240 100\" style=\"flex: 1;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-kid=\"92\">\n                    <defs data-kid=\"93\">\n                      <linearGradient id=\"chartGrad\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"0\" y2=\"1\" data-kid=\"94\">\n                        <stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#62e6ff\" stop-opacity=\"0.3\" data-kid=\"95\"></stop>\n                        <stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#62e6ff\" stop-opacity=\"0\" data-kid=\"96\"></stop>\n                      </linearGradient>\n                    </defs>\n                    <path d=\"M0,80 L30,70 L60,60 L90,50 L120,55 L150,35 L180,25 L210,20 L240,10 L240,100 L0,100 Z\" fill=\"url(#chartGrad)\" data-kid=\"97\"></path>\n                    <path d=\"M0,80 L30,70 L60,60 L90,50 L120,55 L150,35 L180,25 L210,20 L240,10\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#62e6ff\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"98\"></path>\n                    <circle cx=\"240\" cy=\"10\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#62e6ff\" data-kid=\"99\"></circle>\n                  </svg>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section style=\"padding: 120px 40px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\" data-kid=\"100\">\n    <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(98,230,255,0.3), transparent);\" data-kid=\"101\"></div>\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;\" data-kid=\"102\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px;\" data-kid=\"103\">\n        <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\" data-kid=\"104\">Como funciona</div>\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 44px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; line-height: 1.1;\" data-kid=\"105\">Três passos para encontrar seu<br data-kid=\"106\">próximo produto vencedor.</h2>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 40px 1fr 40px 1fr; align-items: start; gap: 0;\" data-kid=\"107\">\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" data-kid=\"108\">\n          <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-kid=\"109\">\n            <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; background: rgba(98,230,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(98,230,255,0.25); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\" data-kid=\"110\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-user-circle\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #62e6ff;\" data-kid=\"111\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 900; color: rgba(98,230,255,0.12); letter-spacing: -0.04em;\" data-kid=\"112\">01</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"113\">Informe seu perfil</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"114\">Descreva seu nicho, marketplace preferido, objetivo e investimento disponível.</p>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;\" data-kid=\"115\">\n            <span class=\"badge badge-electric\" data-kid=\"116\">Shopee</span>\n            <span class=\"badge badge-violet\" data-kid=\"117\">Tecnologia</span>\n            <span class=\"badge\" style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: #94a3b8; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\" data-kid=\"118\">Afiliado</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding-top: 40px;\" data-kid=\"119\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgba(98,230,255,0.4);\" data-kid=\"120\"></i>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" data-kid=\"121\">\n          <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-kid=\"122\">\n            <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.25); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\" data-kid=\"123\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-cpu\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #a78bfa;\" data-kid=\"124\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 900; color: rgba(139,92,246,0.12); letter-spacing: -0.04em;\" data-kid=\"125\">02</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"126\">A IA analisa o mercado</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"127\">Nosso algoritmo compara margem, concorrência, conversão e risco em tempo real.</p>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-direction: column;\" data-kid=\"128\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"129\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" style=\"color: #65f0b7; font-size: 13px;\" data-kid=\"130\"></i> Calculando margem estimada...</div>\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"131\"><i class=\"ti ti-check\" style=\"color: #65f0b7; font-size: 13px;\" data-kid=\"132\"></i> Comparando concorrência...</div>\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #62e6ff; animation: pulse 2s infinite;\" data-kid=\"133\"><i class=\"ti ti-loader-2 ti-spin\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-kid=\"134\"></i> Estimando conversão...</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding-top: 40px;\" data-kid=\"135\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgba(98,230,255,0.4);\" data-kid=\"136\"></i>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" data-kid=\"137\">\n          <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-kid=\"138\">\n            <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; background: rgba(101,240,183,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(101,240,183,0.25); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\" data-kid=\"139\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-trophy\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #65f0b7;\" data-kid=\"140\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 900; color: rgba(101,240,183,0.12); letter-spacing: -0.04em;\" data-kid=\"141\">03</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"142\">Receba o ranking</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"143\">Produtos ordenados por score de oportunidade, com margem, risco e estratégia recomendada.</p>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; background: rgba(101,240,183,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(101,240,183,0.15); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;\" data-kid=\"144\">\n            <span style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #65f0b7; letter-spacing: -0.04em;\" data-kid=\"145\">87</span>\n            <div data-kid=\"146\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #f8fafc;\" data-kid=\"147\">Score de Oportunidade</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"148\">alta margem · baixa concorrência</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section style=\"padding: 80px 40px 120px; position: relative;\" data-kid=\"149\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;\" data-kid=\"150\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px;\" data-kid=\"151\">\n        <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\" data-kid=\"152\">Benefícios</div>\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 44px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; line-height: 1.1;\" data-kid=\"153\">Por que vendedores escolhem<br data-kid=\"154\">o ProductHunter AI</h2>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: auto auto; gap: 16px;\" data-kid=\"155\">\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" style=\"grid-column: 1 / 3; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 48px;\" data-kid=\"156\">\n          \n          <div style=\"flex-shrink: 0; position: relative; width: 160px; height: 160px;\" data-kid=\"157\">\n            <svg width=\"160\" height=\"160\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" data-kid=\"158\">\n              <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\" stroke-width=\"8\" data-kid=\"159\"></circle>\n              <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"40\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#65f0b7\" stroke-width=\"8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-dasharray=\"251\" stroke-dashoffset=\"32\" transform=\"rotate(-90 50 50)\" style=\"filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(101,240,183,0.6))\" data-kid=\"160\"></circle>\n            </svg>\n            <div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\" data-kid=\"161\">\n              <span style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: #65f0b7; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1;\" data-kid=\"162\">87</span>\n              <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"163\">/100</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div data-kid=\"164\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px;\" data-kid=\"165\">\n              <div style=\"width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(101,240,183,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(101,240,183,0.2); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\" data-kid=\"166\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-rosette\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #65f0b7;\" data-kid=\"167\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <h3 style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"168\">Score de Oportunidade</h3>\n            </div>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0 0 16px;\" data-kid=\"169\">Cada produto recebe uma pontuação de 0 a 100 calculada pela nossa IA, considerando margem, demanda, concorrência e risco combinados.</p>\n            <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"170\">\n              <span class=\"badge badge-mint\" data-kid=\"171\">Alta margem</span>\n              <span class=\"badge badge-electric\" data-kid=\"172\">Baixa concorrência</span>\n              <span class=\"badge\" style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: #94a3b8; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\" data-kid=\"173\">Alta conversão</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" data-kid=\"174\">\n          <div style=\"width: 44px; height: 44px; background: rgba(98,230,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(98,230,255,0.2); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px;\" data-kid=\"175\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-chart-bar\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #62e6ff;\" data-kid=\"176\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"177\">Margem estimada antes de comprar</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"178\">Veja a margem potencial de cada produto antes de apostar seu estoque.</p>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 20px;\" data-kid=\"179\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px;\" data-kid=\"180\">\n              <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"181\">Tecnologia</span>\n              <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #65f0b7; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"182\">42%</span>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 100px; height: 6px; overflow: hidden;\" data-kid=\"183\">\n              <div class=\"mini-bar\" style=\"width: 42%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #62e6ff, #65f0b7);\" data-kid=\"184\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 6px;\" data-kid=\"185\">\n              <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"186\">Beleza</span>\n              <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #65f0b7; font-weight: 600;\" data-kid=\"187\">38%</span>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 100px; height: 6px; overflow: hidden;\" data-kid=\"188\">\n              <div class=\"mini-bar\" style=\"width: 38%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #62e6ff, #65f0b7);\" data-kid=\"189\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" data-kid=\"190\">\n          <div style=\"width: 44px; height: 44px; background: rgba(248,184,92,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(248,184,92,0.2); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px;\" data-kid=\"191\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-shield-check\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #f8b85c;\" data-kid=\"192\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"193\">Score de risco para cada produto</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"194\">Avalie riscos antes de investir: saturação, sazonalidade e concorrência analisados.</p>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-direction: column;\" data-kid=\"195\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\" data-kid=\"196\">\n              <span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"197\">Mini impressora</span>\n              <span class=\"badge badge-mint\" data-kid=\"198\">Baixo</span>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\" data-kid=\"199\">\n              <span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"200\">Luminária gamer</span>\n              <span class=\"badge badge-ember\" data-kid=\"201\">Médio</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" style=\"grid-column: 1 / 3;\" data-kid=\"202\">\n          <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-kid=\"203\">\n            <div style=\"width: 44px; height: 44px; background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\" data-kid=\"204\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-chart-dots-3\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #a78bfa;\" data-kid=\"205\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"206\">Comparação entre marketplaces</h3>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 12px; align-items: end;\" data-kid=\"207\">\n            \n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"208\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #65f0b7;\" data-kid=\"209\">89</div>\n              <div style=\"width: 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #65f0b7, rgba(101,240,183,0.3)); border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; height: 80px; transition: all 0.3s;\" data-kid=\"210\"></div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"211\">Shopee</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"212\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #62e6ff;\" data-kid=\"213\">82</div>\n              <div style=\"width: 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #62e6ff, rgba(98,230,255,0.3)); border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; height: 68px; transition: all 0.3s;\" data-kid=\"214\"></div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"215\">Mercado Livre</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"216\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #a78bfa;\" data-kid=\"217\">76</div>\n              <div style=\"width: 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #a78bfa, rgba(139,92,246,0.3)); border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; height: 60px;\" data-kid=\"218\"></div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"219\">Amazon</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"220\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8b85c;\" data-kid=\"221\">71</div>\n              <div style=\"width: 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8b85c, rgba(248,184,92,0.3)); border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; height: 54px;\" data-kid=\"222\"></div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"223\">TikTok Shop</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\" data-kid=\"224\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"225\">64</div>\n              <div style=\"width: 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #94a3b8, rgba(148,163,184,0.2)); border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; height: 46px;\" data-kid=\"226\"></div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"227\">Magalu</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\" data-kid=\"228\">Score de oportunidade médio por marketplace · Nicho: Tecnologia · Atualizado agora</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bento-card\" data-kid=\"229\">\n          <div style=\"width: 44px; height: 44px; background: rgba(98,230,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(98,230,255,0.18); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px;\" data-kid=\"230\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-bolt\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #62e6ff;\" data-kid=\"231\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\" data-kid=\"232\">Produtos com baixa concorrência</h3>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"233\">Descubra oportunidades pouco exploradas antes da concorrência.</p>\n          <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; background: rgba(98,230,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(98,230,255,0.15); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px;\" data-kid=\"234\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #62e6ff; letter-spacing: -0.04em;\" data-kid=\"235\">247</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 2px;\" data-kid=\"236\">produtos com baixa concorrência agora</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section style=\"padding: 80px 40px 120px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); position: relative;\" data-kid=\"237\">\n    <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(101,240,183,0.3), transparent);\" data-kid=\"238\"></div>\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;\" data-kid=\"239\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 52px;\" data-kid=\"240\">\n        <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\" data-kid=\"241\">Demonstração</div>\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 44px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: #f8fafc; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.1;\" data-kid=\"242\">Veja na prática</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"243\">Exemplo real para: Vendedor + Shopee + Tecnologia</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 32px;\" data-kid=\"244\">\n        <div class=\"glass-strong\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 14px; border-color: rgba(98,230,255,0.2);\" data-kid=\"245\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-user\" style=\"color: #62e6ff; font-size: 16px;\" data-kid=\"246\"></i>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #f8fafc; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"247\">Vendedor</span>\n          <span style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\" data-kid=\"248\">·</span>\n          <i class=\"ti ti-shopping-bag\" style=\"color: #65f0b7; font-size: 16px;\" data-kid=\"249\"></i>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #f8fafc; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"250\">Shopee</span>\n          <span style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\" data-kid=\"251\">·</span>\n          <i class=\"ti ti-device-laptop\" style=\"color: #a78bfa; font-size: 16px;\" data-kid=\"252\"></i>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #f8fafc; font-weight: 500;\" data-kid=\"253\">Tecnologia</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;\" data-kid=\"254\">\n        \n        <div style=\"background: rgba(101,240,183,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(101,240,183,0.2); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\" data-kid=\"255\">\n          <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; width: 200px; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(101,240,183,0.03)); pointer-events: none;\" data-kid=\"256\"></div>\n          <div style=\"width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(101,240,183,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(101,240,183,0.3); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"257\">\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #65f0b7;\" data-kid=\"258\">01</span>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"flex: 1;\" data-kid=\"259\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 4px;\" data-kid=\"260\">\n              <span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; letter-spacing: -0.01em;\" data-kid=\"261\">Mini impressora térmica portátil</span>\n              <span class=\"badge badge-mint\" style=\"font-size: 10px; padding: 3px 8px;\" data-kid=\"262\">Produto Vencedor</span>\n            </div>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"263\">\"Boa margem, produto leve, alta procura e concorrência moderada.\"</p>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;\" data-kid=\"264\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-kid=\"265\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\" data-kid=\"266\">SCORE</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #65f0b7; letter-spacing: -0.03em;\" data-kid=\"267\">87</div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-alig